<D>__{oh. thank you, lucy.}
<A>__{gru accepts the lipstick taser.}
<C>__{silas }
<D>__{agent wilde!}
<A>__{lucy ignores this and just waits, not wanting to leave. she and gru stand there awkwardly.}
<C>__{gru}
<D>__{well... it looks like they need you, so...}
